title: wgDownloader 3.0.0.20 pre-patched + patcher
description:
wgDownloader has already been patched with the patcher, so there's no need to run the patcher unless you want to patch another/older/newer version, it'll probably work, just need to decompress the binary first with UPX


The patch is purely functional, there's no changes to the GUI, even though it says 'FREE', etc, it functions like PRO. Too lazy to figure out why it doesn't want to display PRO ;)



Run wgDownloader.exe and enjoy! Patcher by the fuzzy red fox / fuzzfox! o/ :3



Virustotal scan for the patcher 
https://www.virustotal.com/en/file/fd9e35108896c4e4115d0937972c52cf33690defd80687f79fb07da607db83fb/analysis/1447283936/


-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Downloading of large galleries from Tumblr, Flickr, Imagefap a thousands others with a one click. No more endless clicking and right clicking to "save image as". Application is optimalized to download large galleries- 50 000 photos in gallery is not problem. Just enter url of webpage with images and make coffee, application makes all hard work for you. You can export all images links to external file, create bookmarks to quick access to your favorite galleries and start fullscreen slideshow for gallery images.
